<div class="container-xxl py-5" id="appVue">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-0 gx-5 align-items-end">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="section-header text-start mb-5 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s"
                     style="max-width: 500px">
                    <h1 class="display-5 mb-3">甜點品項</h1>
                    @*<button class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="fas fa-pen text-primary"></i></button>*@
                    <p>
                        嘴裡吃點甜讓生活帶些甜
                        因長期自體免疫狀況及經常在小兒科打滾(?!)，漸漸深知《原食材》對我們的重要性，因此在製作甜點時，不使用防腐劑、香精、膨鬆劑…等化學添加，不僅使用原食材，也堅持好食材，來呈現天然的美味。
                        🍑🍍甜點裡所用各式果醬，也均是親自熬煮而成。
                        🌡️唯有造型蛋糕，因外觀裝飾調色問題，得用少許食用色素。(均進口且符合食安標準)
                        甜甜們減糖也減油，相對保存期限也較短，一律採「接單後製作」無法「即訂現取」🙅
                        👯交期除非有特別指定日期(請私訊詢問)，均排單出貨喔，有時單量大可能需等上1~2個月，請耐心等候。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-start text-lg-end wow slideInRight" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <ul class="nav nav-pills d-inline-flex justify-content-end mb-5">
                    <li class="nav-item me-2">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary border-2 active" data-bs-toggle="pill"
                           href="#tab-1">常備品項</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item me-2">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary border-2" data-bs-toggle="pill" href="#tab-2">
                            泡芙
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item me-0">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary border-2" data-bs-toggle="pill" href="#tab-3">季節限定</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-content">
            <div id="tab-1" class="tab-pane fade show p-0 active">
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" v-for="i in ProductInfo">



                        <div class="product-item">
                            <div class="position-relative bg-light overflow-hidden" @@click="toPD">
                                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="productDetail" class="nav-item nav-link active">
                                    <div>
                                        <img class="img-fluid w-100" :src=`/img/${i.imageName}` :alt="i.productName" :title=`${i.productName}-${i.specifications}` />
                                    </div>
                                </a>

                                <div class="bg-secondary rounded text-white position-absolute start-0 top-0 m-4 py-1 px-3">
                                    tag只留狗狗可食跟含酒
                                </div>
                                @*<button class="rounded-pill bg-light text-primary position-absolute end-0 top-0 m-4 py-1 px-3 momo-off-shelve">
                                下架
                                </button>*@
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center p-4">

                                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="productDetail" class="nav-item nav-link active">{{i.productName}}</a>
                                <span class="text-primary me-1">${{i.price}}</span>
                                <span class="text-primary me-1">{{i.specifications}}</span>
                                <!-- <span class="text-body text-decoration-line-through">$29.00</span> -->
